haberman.rhizomatics.data

Class Sound

  • java.lang.Object
    • haberman.rhizomatics.data.Sound

  • public class Sound
extends java.lang.Object
    This class describes every aspect of a sound on a MapContainer. It works in pair with PolySound.

             int peels_size)
        Constructor for Sound.ShapeType.POLYGON type. This object needs most of its internals to be constructed.
        Parameters:
        id - The RawRes id
        volume_type - The VolumeType
        title - The title
        colors - An array of colors for linear gradient interpolation
        sustain - The maximum radius (in meters) of for the sustain volume of the corresponding PolySound
        points - An array of locations for the area where this sound could be listened to
        growth_start - Where to start peels' poly generation (as a ratio between inner and outer)
        growth_end - Where to end peels' poly generation
        peels_size - The amount of poly to generate
